    "The search query was TS = (Digital transformation AND SME), with a search period from \"2015 to 2023,\" yielding a total of 81 pertinent documents.",
    "Following retrieval, the literature underwent a meticulous reassessment to exclude book reviews, conference abstracts, and irrelevant documents.",
    "A comprehensive compilation of bibliographic information was also conducted, encompassing titles, authors, abstracts, publication sources, keywords, references, and regions.",
    "This research recognizes the utmost importance of data quality and relevance in ensuring the strength of the analysis while also carefully selecting foreign literature from the \"Web of Science\" database.",
